<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Intercom Generate</title>
    <script src="/scripts.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/style.css"/>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.ico">

  </head>

  <body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-inverse">
      <div class="container">
          <p><a class="navbar-brand" href="/" ><img src="https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/71995579/7e8e462dee5d13c376ab8aa1/logo.png"> | 🏭 Generate</a></p>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container" id="intro">
      <p>Generate sample users and conversations for your test app. If multiple people are using this at once it will break down and fall over. Try waiting 2 minutes and trying again.</p>
      <p>Reach out to <strong><a style="text-decoration:none" href="https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/72003015/3ca6c3cd4149460cff954dd5/awesome.gif" target="_blank">@chris</a></strong> on Slack if you run into problems or have feedback on other features that you'd find useful. Here's some links to help get your access token!
        <ul>
          <li>Find Your Token <a href="https://app.intercom.io/a/apps/_/developer-hub">here</a></li>
          <li>Confirm Your Installation <a href="https://app.intercom.com/a/apps/_/settings/web">here</a>.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="container">
      <form method="POST" action="/seed">
          <div class="form-group">
            <h2>Generate Users</h2>
            <label>Personal Access Token:</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="pat">
          </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Generate 100 Users 🥁</button>
      </form>
    <hr>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Generate Conversations</h2>
      <form method="POST" action="/conversations">
          <div class="form-group">
            <p>Make sure you have already generated some users before trying to create conversations! :)
            <label>Personal Access Token:</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="pat">
          </div>
          <div class="btn-group" data-toggle="button">
            <label class="btn btn-primary active">
              <input type="radio" name="role" id="CSR_button" value="CSR" autocomplete="off"> CSR
            </label>
            <label class="btn btn-primary">
              <input type="radio" name="role" id="CSE_button" value="CSE" autocomplete="off"> CSE
            </label>
            <label class="btn btn-primary">
              <input type="radio" name="role" id="CSL_button" value="CSL" autocomplete="off"> CSL
            </label>
          </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Generate Convos 🗣</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <!-- Example row of columns -->
      <hr>
      <footer>
      <a onclick="/scripts.js"><button id="button">Button!</button></a>
      </footer>
    </div> <!-- /container -->
  </body>
</html>
